</div>

<div id="aboutmodal" class="modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" data-show="true" style="color:#333;">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h4 class="modal-title">Power/Money/Science</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>This is the website for the interactive, multi-player puzzle game that I built for my 2017 Halloween party. The party is over, but the software remains.</p>
                <p>If you'd like to simulate the game-play experience you will need to load the Central Display into a browser tab and leave it running while you create your own player character (by clicking one of the three company logos at the bottom of this page).</p>
                <p><a href="/Central" class=" btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Central Display</a></p>
                <p>This game was designed to be played by a large group of people in the same physical area. Your experience may vary.</p>
            </div>

                @*<div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" id="dropItem"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-wrench"></span> Drop Item</button>
                </div>*@
        </div>
    </div>
</div>